
  - ------ - ------- - ------- - -- --------- ----- 
   The Law
  - ------ - ------- - ------- - -- --------- -----

   The Law are a group of mortals who have progressed
   through the ranks of the Servants and are given 
   the ability to Freeze, Demote, or Promote those
   who they see fit to suffer or succeed at Shardak's
   hand.  The Law will hear all issues and form an
   elite band who will deal those who stray from
   the path Shardak wishes to draw for us...

   THE LAW:  Undetermined

